Gineko is a code search extension for GitHub, available for Chrome.

Features 🔥
🔎 Search Code : Press Cmd+Shift+F to quickly search over all files in the currently branch.
🗂 Jump Files: Press Cmd+/ to open file list and let you navigate to any file
🎨 Support Dark Theme and Rich icons
↔️  Resizable layout

Personal data 🔒
Gineko had never collected and will never collect any personal data, browsing history, etc. Gineko also doesn't share/care about your data at all.
